      class  RosSrvMessageAddress
      Gson object class: A class of a rosSrvMessageAddress with its "args"(for service call) typed as the Address string, and its "values"(roe service response) typed as a int32, 0 for not received and 1 for received
      class  RosSrvMessageGenReport
      Gson object class: A class of a rosSrvMessage with its "args"(for service call) typed as the command string, and its "values"(ros service response) typed as a int32, 0 for not generated and 1 for generated
